Richard Dawkins: 'I Am Offended!'


On March 8th, 2008, Richard Dawkins gave a lecture on &quot;The God Delusion&quot; during 

his US Tour. The event took place on the UC Berkeley campus in Wheeler Auditorium,

 and was completely sold out. 

A line of hopeful attendees stretched around the side of the building, waiting to see if there would be any &quot;no-show&quot; tickets at the last minute!


Visit http://www.richarddawkins.net/



